<h2>Analysis</h2>
<p1>I did my interview with my grandfather Nick Poole. My grandfather has accomplished a lot in his life, before he created Caxton Mark, he was a part owner in a company called Mapple Roll Leaf which when the owners all agreed to sell the company he got a large portion of. He used his Money to start up Caxton Mark which is now a large business that deals with almost every country in the world.




