<div id="Movie Reffrence">
<h1> Movie Reffrence</h1>
<h2>Lone Survivor</h2>
<p>Summary: The movie I chose was lone survivor. The movie lone survivor is about 4 men in the NAVY SEALs that were tasked with a task to do some recon on a village that the military believed was where a wanted taliban leader who had murdered many Americans was located. They climbed up mountains and did some recon from there but they unexpectedly ran into some goat herders and they decided to let the goat herders go which meant they had to abandon mission as the goat herders would obviously run down to tell the Taliban. After a Few Hours the 4 men come into contact with 100's of Taliban fighters and an all out firefight followed, it ended with 3 of the four men dead and the last man was saved by some afghans who supported the Americans.</p>   

    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
